'''Gisimenti''' ni ahantu hazwi cyane mu mujyi wa Kigali<ref><nowiki>https://www.afrik21.africa/en/rwanda-self-service-electric-bicycles-approved-in-kigali/#navbarToggler1</nowiki></ref>. Hazwi kw'izina rya [[Kigali]] Car Free Zone<ref><nowiki>https://vymaps.com/RW/Gisimenti-218950898241892/</nowiki></ref>.
Gisimenti iherereye mu murenge wa Remera, hafi ya [[Stade Amahoro]] aha hantu uhasanga ibikorwa byu bucuruzi byinshi<ref><nowiki>https://allafrica.com/stories/202202230190.html</nowiki></ref>,  nki cyicaro gikuru cya Airtel mu [[Rwanda]],Lando hoteri, Banki ya Kigali,Zigama Bank, ishami rya MTN.
Gisimenti abantu bahurira hamwe bagamije kwishimisha<ref><nowiki>https://taarifa.rw/stromae-thrills-at-victoires-de-la-musique-show/</nowiki></ref> bagendeye kubyo bakunda<ref><nowiki>https://mobile.igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/gisimenti-ni-sodoma-mu-isura-nshya-cyangwa-ni-imyidagaduro-yaziye-igihe</nowiki></ref>. Gisimenti yamenyekane cyane kubikorwa bihakorerwa mu masaha ya nijoro.
Ibyabereye <ref><nowiki>https://umuryango.rw/imyidagaduro/article/hagereranywa-n-ikuzimu-gisimenti-ikomeje-kurikoroza-bamwe-basaba-ko-hafungwa</nowiki></ref>Gisimenti mu masaha ya nijoro byagiye bivugwa cyane
mubinyamakuru byandika no ku mbuga nkoranyambaga.<ref><nowiki>https://umuryango.rw/imyidagaduro/article/nyuma-y-amashusho-y-urukozasoni-ku-gisimenti-hafatiwe-ingamba-zikakaye</nowiki></ref>

